q1_MonthlyIncome=df['MonthlyIncome'].quantile(0.25)
q3_MonthlyIncome=df['MonthlyIncome'].quantile(0.75)
IQR_MonthlyIncome=q3_MonthlyIncome-q1_MonthlyIncome
lowerbound_MonthlyIncome=q1_MonthlyIncome-1.5*IQR_MonthlyIncome
upperbound_MonthlyIncome=q3_MonthlyIncome+1.5*IQR_MonthlyIncome
df['MonthlyIncome']=np.where(df['MonthlyIncome']>=upperbound_MonthlyIncome,df['MonthlyIncome'].median(),df['MonthlyIncome'])

q1_NumCompaniesWorked=df['NumCompaniesWorked'].quantile(0.25)
q3_NumCompaniesWorked=df['NumCompaniesWorked'].quantile(0.75)
IQR_NumCompaniesWorked=q3_NumCompaniesWorked-q1_NumCompaniesWorked
lowerbound_NumCompaniesWorked=q1_NumCompaniesWorked-1.5*IQR_NumCompaniesWorked
